claim.claim-text:
1. A computer-implemented method, comprising:
defining one or more personalized categories, wherein each personalized category comprises one or more terms;
identifying at least one of said one or more personalized categories that is associated with a user query;
identifying one or more terms that are associated with said user query and with said at least one identified personalized category;
adding said identified one or more terms to said user query, thereby creating an expanded query; and
presenting the expanded query to the user for at least one of acceptance of the expanded query, rejection of the expanded query, and modification of the expanded query.

6. An apparatus comprising:
one or more memories that store computer-readable code; and
one or more processors operatively coupled to the one or more memories, the one or more processors configured to implement the computer-readable code, the computer-readable code configured to:
define one or more personalized categories, wherein each personalized category comprises one or more terms;
identify at least one of said one or more personalized categories that is associated with a user query;
identify one or more terms that are associated with said user query and with said at least one identified personalized category;
add said identified one or more terms to said user query, thereby creating an expanded query; and
present the expanded query to the user for at least one of acceptance of the expanded query, rejection of the expanded query, and modification of the expanded query.
